<item>
            <title>[LU-14073] Support for linux kernel version 5.9</title>
                <link>https://jira.whamcloud.com/browse/LU-14073</link>
                <project id="10000" key="LU">Lustre</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Now that Linux 5.9 is in released it makes sense to support compiling against it&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;p&gt;This requires:&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;ldiskfs patch updates to follow kernel extt4 changes.&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;removal of smp_read_barrier_depends() which no longer exists&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Fix autoconf check for clean_bdev_aliases which no longer works&lt;/li&gt;
	&lt;li&gt;Remove dependence on seqment_eq() which no longer exits.&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
</description>
